{"id":153,"ayahs":[{"number":23,"arabic":"قَالَا رَبَّنَا ظَلَمْنَآ أَنفُسَنَا وَإِن لَّمْ تَغْفِرْ لَنَا وَتَرْحَمْنَا لَنَكُونَنَّ مِنَ ٱلْخَٰسِرِينَ","translation":"The two replied: \"O our Sustainer! We have sinned against ourselves -and unless Thou grant us forgiveness and bestow Thy mercy upon us, we shall most certainly be lost!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/977.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":26452,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَا","translation":"(আদম ও হাওয়া) দু'জনে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26453,"position":2,"arabic":"رَبَّنَا","translation":"\"হে আমাদের রব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26454,"position":3,"arabic":"ظَلَمْنَآ","translation":"অন্যায় করেছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26455,"position":4,"arabic":"أَنفُسَنَا","translation":"আমাদের নিজেদের (উপর)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26456,"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26457,"position":6,"arabic":"لَّمْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26458,"position":7,"arabic":"تَغْفِرْ","translation":"ক্ষমা করো তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26459,"position":8,"arabic":"لَنَا","translation":"আমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26460,"position":9,"arabic":"وَتَرْحَمْنَا","translation":"ও আমাদেরকে দয়া (না) করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26461,"position":10,"arabic":"لَنَكُونَنَّ","translation":"অবশ্যই  আমরা হবো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26462,"position":11,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26463,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْخَـٰسِرِينَ","translation":"ক্ষতিগ্রস্তদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_023_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26464,"position":13,"arabic":"٢٣","translation":"(২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":24,"arabic":"قَالَ ٱهْبِطُوا۟ بَعْضُكُمْ لِبَعْضٍ عَدُوٌّۭ ۖ وَلَكُمْ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ مُسْتَقَرٌّۭ وَمَتَٰعٌ إِلَىٰ حِينٍۢ","translation":"Said He: \"Down with you, [and be henceforth] enemies unto one another, having on earth your abode and livelihood for a while:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/978.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":27449,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(আল্লাহ) বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27450,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱهْبِطُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা নেমে যাও","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27451,"position":3,"arabic":"بَعْضُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের একে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27452,"position":4,"arabic":"لِبَعْضٍ","translation":"জন্যে অপরের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27453,"position":5,"arabic":"عَدُوٌّۭ ۖ","translation":"শত্রু","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27455,"position":6,"arabic":"وَلَكُمْ","translation":"এবং জন্যে  তোমাদের (থাকবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27456,"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27457,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27458,"position":9,"arabic":"مُسْتَقَرٌّۭ","translation":"অবস্থান","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27459,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَتَـٰعٌ","translation":"ও জীবন সামগ্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27460,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"পর্যন্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27461,"position":12,"arabic":"حِينٍۢ","translation":"নির্দিষ্ট সময়\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_024_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27462,"position":13,"arabic":"٢٤","translation":"(২৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":25,"arabic":"قَالَ فِيهَا تَحْيَوْنَ وَفِيهَا تَمُوتُونَ وَمِنْهَا تُخْرَجُونَ","translation":"there shall you live\" - He added - \"and there shall you die, and thence shall you be brought forth [on Resurrection Day]!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/979.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":28512,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"তিনি বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_025_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28513,"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهَا","translation":"\"মধ্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_025_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28514,"position":3,"arabic":"تَحْيَوْنَ","translation":"জীবিত থাকবে তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_025_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28515,"position":4,"arabic":"وَفِيهَا","translation":"ও মধ্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_025_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28516,"position":5,"arabic":"تَمُوتُونَ","translation":"মৃত্যুবরণ করবে তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_025_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28517,"position":6,"arabic":"وَمِنْهَا","translation":"ও থেকে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_025_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28518,"position":7,"arabic":"تُخْرَجُونَ","translation":"তোমাদের বের করা হবে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_025_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28519,"position":8,"arabic":"٢٥","translation":"(২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":26,"arabic":"يَٰبَنِىٓ ءَادَمَ قَدْ أَنزَلْنَا عَلَيْكُمْ لِبَاسًۭا يُوَٰرِى سَوْءَٰتِكُمْ وَرِيشًۭا ۖ وَلِبَاسُ ٱلتَّقْوَىٰ ذَٰلِكَ خَيْرٌۭ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ مِنْ ءَايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ لَعَلَّهُمْ يَذَّكَّرُونَ","translation":"O CHILDREN of Adam! Indeed, We have bestowed upon you from on high [the knowledge of making] garments to cover your nakedness, and as a thing of beauty: but the garment of God-consciousness is the best of all. Herein lies a message from God, so that man” might take it to heart.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/980.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":29449,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰبَنِىٓ","translation":"হে সন্তান","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29450,"position":2,"arabic":"ءَادَمَ","translation":"আদমের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29451,"position":3,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29452,"position":4,"arabic":"أَنزَلْنَا","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29453,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"উপর তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29454,"position":6,"arabic":"لِبَاسًۭا","translation":"পোশাক","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29455,"position":7,"arabic":"يُوَٰرِى","translation":"তা ঢেকে রাখে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29456,"position":8,"arabic":"سَوْءَٰتِكُمْ","translation":"লজ্জাস্থানগুলো তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29457,"position":9,"arabic":"وَرِيشًۭا ۖ","translation":"ও শোভা বর্ধকরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29459,"position":10,"arabic":"وَلِبَاسُ","translation":"ও পোশাক","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29460,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلتَّقْوَىٰ","translation":"তাকওয়ার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29461,"position":12,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটাই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29462,"position":13,"arabic":"خَيْرٌۭ ۚ","translation":"উত্তম","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29464,"position":14,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29465,"position":15,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29466,"position":16,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتِ","translation":"নিদর্শনাবলীর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29467,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29468,"position":18,"arabic":"لَعَلَّهُمْ","translation":"সম্ভবতঃ তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29469,"position":19,"arabic":"يَذَّكَّرُونَ","translation":"শিক্ষা গ্রহন করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_026_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29470,"position":20,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"يَٰبَنِىٓ ءَادَمَ لَا يَفْتِنَنَّكُمُ ٱلشَّيْطَٰنُ كَمَآ أَخْرَجَ أَبَوَيْكُم مِّنَ ٱلْجَنَّةِ يَنزِعُ عَنْهُمَا لِبَاسَهُمَا لِيُرِيَهُمَا سَوْءَٰتِهِمَآ ۗ إِنَّهُۥ يَرَىٰكُمْ هُوَ وَقَبِيلُهُۥ مِنْ حَيْثُ لَا تَرَوْنَهُمْ ۗ إِنَّا جَعَلْنَا ٱلشَّيَٰطِينَ أَوْلِيَآءَ لِلَّذِينَ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"O children of Adam! Do not allow Satan to seduce you in the same way as he caused your ancestors to be driven out of the garden: he deprived them of their garment [of God-consciousness] in order to make them aware of their nakedness. Verily, he and his tribe are lying in wait for you where you cannot perceive them! Verily, We have placed [all manner of] satanic forces near unto those who do not [truly] believe;","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/981.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":30443,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰبَنِىٓ","translation":"হে সন্তান","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30444,"position":2,"arabic":"ءَادَمَ","translation":"আদমের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30445,"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30446,"position":4,"arabic":"يَفْتِنَنَّكُمُ","translation":"তোমাদের পরীক্ষায় ফেলে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30447,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنُ","translation":"শয়তান","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30448,"position":6,"arabic":"كَمَآ","translation":"যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30449,"position":7,"arabic":"أَخْرَجَ","translation":"সে বের করেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30450,"position":8,"arabic":"أَبَوَيْكُم","translation":"পিতা-মাতাকে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30451,"position":9,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30452,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةِ","translation":"জান্নাত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30453,"position":11,"arabic":"يَنزِعُ","translation":"খুলে ফেলে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30454,"position":12,"arabic":"عَنْهُمَا","translation":"থেকে তাদের দু'জন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30455,"position":13,"arabic":"لِبَاسَهُمَا","translation":"পোষাক তাদের দু'জনের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30456,"position":14,"arabic":"لِيُرِيَهُمَا","translation":"জন্যে তাদের দু'জনকে দেখানোর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30457,"position":15,"arabic":"سَوْءَٰتِهِمَآ ۗ","translation":"লজ্জাস্থান তাদের দু'জনের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30459,"position":16,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই সে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30460,"position":17,"arabic":"يَرَىٰكُمْ","translation":"দেখে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30461,"position":18,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"সে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30462,"position":19,"arabic":"وَقَبِيلُهُۥ","translation":"ও দলবল তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30463,"position":20,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30464,"position":21,"arabic":"حَيْثُ","translation":"যেখান","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30465,"position":22,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30466,"position":23,"arabic":"تَرَوْنَهُمْ ۗ","translation":"তোমরা দেখো তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30468,"position":24,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30469,"position":25,"arabic":"جَعَلْنَا","translation":"আমরা বানিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30470,"position":26,"arabic":"ٱلشَّيَـٰطِينَ","translation":"শয়তানদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30471,"position":27,"arabic":"أَوْلِيَآءَ","translation":"অভিভাবকরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30472,"position":28,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) জন্যে যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30473,"position":29,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30474,"position":30,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_027_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30475,"position":31,"arabic":"٢٧","translation":"(২৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":28,"arabic":"وَإِذَا فَعَلُوا۟ فَٰحِشَةًۭ قَالُوا۟ وَجَدْنَا عَلَيْهَآ ءَابَآءَنَا وَٱللَّهُ أَمَرَنَا بِهَا ۗ قُلْ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ لَا يَأْمُرُ بِٱلْفَحْشَآءِ ۖ أَتَقُولُونَ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ مَا لَا تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"and [so,] whenever they commit a shameful deed, they are wont to say, \"We found our forefathers doing it,\" and, \"God has enjoined it upon us.\" Say: \"Behold, never does God enjoin deeds of abomination. Would